manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: YABER U10 Native 1080P Projector - Upgraded Projector with WiFi and Bluetooth 2023 Why choose our YABER U10 projector? Why we are special？ Compatible with 4K & 1080P Native Resolution: Equipped with the Yaber Basic 2.0 chip& high transmittance and refraction of lens, more of the image's original details and color are retained during image processing. The Yaber home projector delivers greater clarity and brighter images. 15000L Higher Brightness: The newly upgraded Yaber U10 projector has a superb level of brightness that allows it to be used even in a room with curtains drawn during the day and for an even more extreme viewing experience at night. Works as a Bluetooth Speaker: Built-in the latest bidirectional Bluetooth 5.1 chip and stereo surround speaker, which not only can connect your Bluetooth speakers wireless but also can be connected to the mobile phone as a speaker at any time freely. Let's experience the immersive audio-visual feast with the Yaber U10 home theater projector！

What is BASIC Smart Engine？Is it Worth? BASIC Smart Engine is a creative projection technology developed by Yaber, through which the best audio-visual experience can be obtained in five aspects——Brightness, Abundant Color, Sound effect, Immersive Display, Clarity. Brightness——The function of the "BASIC" smart engine is to minimize the loss of reflected light, thereby increasing the brightness by 25% than all other 1080P LCD Projectors. Abundant Color——The BASIC Smart Engine technology enables the YABER projector to achieve full-color gamut coverage, making the picture more colorful and natural. Sound Effect——The BASIC Smart Engine technology can make the sound of the Yaber projector more outstanding and pleasant, achieving surround sound or stereo effects. Immersive Display——The imaging of the YABER projector can reach up to 300 inches (Different models, different projection sizes). The joy of getting the whole wall! Clarity——The YABER smart engine can clearly display the details of the image and its boundaries. Step into the world of Full HD!

50% Digital Zoom & 4P Keystone Correction, Take the Hassle Out of Adjustments YABER U10 home projector can use the remote control to select "Digital Zoom" to reduce the image up to 50% of the original length and width with the remote. At the same time, thanks to the 4P Keystone Correction function, all four angles of the picture can all be adjusted individually instead of only along the horizontal or vertical direction, making it more convenient and flexible. With these innovative features, users do not need to frequently adjust the projector distance to match the screen size or move the projector direction to get a circumferential picture.

High-Speed 5G WiFi, Goodbye to Lagging Delay YABER home projector can mirror movies/photos/games from smartphones or other devices to the big screen wireless via WIFI. Say bye to freeze problem, YABER U10 WIFI projector brings smooth giant images to you. Native Resolution: 1920*1080 (Support 4K)Brightness: 15000 LumenContrast Ratio: 20000:1Aspect Ratio: 4:3/16:9/AutoConnection type: Wireless /WiredProjection Size: 45-300"( Optimum is 120")Zoom Function: 100% -50% (Reduced-50%)Keystone Correction: 4-Point Digital Keystone Correction

Warming Tips Is Netflix/ Prime Video supported on this projector with wifi and bluetooth? Due to HDCP copyright, mobile devices cannot mirror the content of some streaming services (Netflix, Amazon, Hulu, etc.), but you could use amazon fire stick to enjoy over 1 million movies and TV episodes. Why is there no sound when playing videos？ When connect the TV stick, please disable Dolby Digital Plus. In other cases, please select a non-Dolby sound source. Any questions, please please please feel free to let us know, we will try our best to give you a best solution!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Impressed with projector quality
reviews.reviewText: Our TV is 10+ year old already, so we started shopping for replacement. Came across this projector with positive YouTuber review and decided to give it a try.This projector was very easy to install and set up. We were very impressed with its image quality. The only downside was the noice from cooling fan. Can be noticeable when turned on, but once it started playing movie/show, it was ok. I think as long as it’s placed further from sofa then it’s ok.I would recommend to anyone who plan to set up home theater. Having a large screen to watch movie with family is super fun.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 23, 2022
reviews.reviewText: This Yaber projector is a great value and the picture quality is very good. It uses the LED technology so it performs well even in rooms with some light leakage when the shades are closed (see the attached images). I am projecting onto a closed window shade for a large window in my bedroom.The keystone function works well as long as all of the projector feet are on a flat surface. The controls allow adjustment of angle and offset and I was able to achieve a rectangular picture even though I set up the projector to the bottom right of the center of the screen. The zoom feature allowed me to install the projector in an ideal location across the room so I scaled it down from there a bit.I used it with my Nvidia Shield TV device over HDMI to get all the content apps and it works well. Everything is HD quality. Bluetooth audio works well with Sony WH headphones.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 11, 2022
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I have another projector and have been happy with it. I got the updated model to see if there was a difference. WOW was I surprised! the quality of the picture and color was obvious right from the start up screen. I honestly did not expect much of a difference and was completely surprised. although I have been happy with the older one, this new one will be my go to projector. I took videos to compare the two. the first one is the older one in the evening. the second one is the updated model during the day. I would definitely recommend buying this one if your looking for a projector. side note, I have had to contact yaber a few times in the past, just with some general questions. They have great customer service and have always responded within 24 hours. I wish all companies were as easy to work with.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 27, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really Bright. Easy-To-Use. Lots of Nice Extras.
reviews.reviewText: We already have an older model Yaber projector and have had it for a few years and decided to upgrade to this unit. We already had a 5 star opinion of the original model and this one so surpassed it that I would give ten stars if I could.This unit, besides looking sleeker, cleaner, and more modern (it kinda looks like the head off that AI robot from the old Portal Games), it is also significantly quieter (the other one's fan was MUCH louder) and atleast twice as bright. In fact, unlike older models, this one is so bright that it is easy to forget that you are looking at a projection at all and not a new LED television. In fact, we project against a white painted plywood wall and it is so bright you cannot even tell that there is a texture of grain to the wall at all. It literally looks like a top quality television, except so enormous that you could never get such a big screen without shelling-out atleast twice as much as this unit costs, if not more. It literally fills our whole wall!Further, this unit was very easy to set-up and use, the menu was easier to navigate than previous models and our small children have no difficultly getting it running to toss in a movie for nap time or for our family evening sit-downs.Perhaps the most pleasant surprise of the whole package is all the EXTRAS it came with! It came with an extra HDMI cord, an extra AV cable, an awesome full-size back-pack style carrying case, a cleaning kit, and a cool lense cover.Its also very sustainable, we live off of solar panels for our electricity and so we have to be very diligent in keeping track of our usage and the draw of electronics on our system, and I can say that this thing can run all day without killing our electric supply. Such can't be said about most other electronics.Very pleased with the unit, it makes our family movie nights complete and we haven't even begun to explore all the extra features, such as using it with our phones etc.The picture i've attached shows the unit I am reviewing (white) here on top of our Xbox One and below the older Yaber unit (black) we've have for several years.The other picture is the display on the wall which is almost 20 feet away, on rough plywood that had been given a coat of white paint (all the seams and textures are still there), and in the middle of the DAY (when projectors work the least)!!!! So, this is the absolute worst projecting conditions for a clear screen, and as you can see, its awesome!!! Not to mention that the size of that projected image of the menu is around10 feet by 10 feet is size!!!
